project_starter_prompt.user_prompt_template:
I need help starting a C++ programming assignment. Here are the details:

ASSIGNMENT: {assignment_type}
DESCRIPTION: {description}
REQUIREMENTS: {requirements}
GRADING CRITERIA: {grading_criteria}

Please help me:
1. Understand what the assignment requires
2. Plan my implementation approach
3. Identify key classes and functions I need to create
4. Understand how my code will be evaluated
5. Get tips for writing high-quality, well-graded code

Be specific and provide concrete examples where helpful.
